00:35:49,150 --> 00:35:51,620
than the prosecutors working alone?

503
00:35:51,650 --> 00:35:53,796
Will the investigation speed
up after a joint HQ is formed?

504
00:35:53,820 --> 00:35:56,130
- It was my mom.
- The expectations are rising.

505
00:35:56,190 --> 00:35:58,660
Every single person they
just named owes my mother.

506
00:35:59,600 --> 00:36:01,836
Among those newly
assigned to headquarters

507
00:36:01,860 --> 00:36:04,020
is Prosecutor Kim Jung Woo
of Seoul Southern Office...

508
00:36:04,670 --> 00:36:05,970
So my mother's making her move.

509
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:09,316
He was a key member of the task force

510
00:36:09,340 --> 00:36:11,640
that took down a major drug distributor...

511
00:36:13,940 --> 00:36:15,010
Start with the office.

512
00:36:16,180 --> 00:36:19,450
- The office.
- Wait a minute. What is all this?

513
00:36:19,850 --> 00:36:20,950
Hey, hold on!

514
00:36:25,660 --> 00:36:27,566
What do you think you're doing?

515
00:36:27,590 --> 00:36:30,730
You're Attorney Kang Shin Jae,
CEO of the LnJ law firm, correct?

516
00:36:31,430 --> 00:36:32,950
We're from the Joint Investigation HQ.

517
00:36:34,700 --> 00:36:36,976
You're under suspicion
for obstructing justice,

518
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:39,300
and illegally obtaining
evidence against Park Je Yeol.

519
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:41,616
We'll now begin a search and seizure

520
00:36:41,640 --> 00:36:44,040
- of all the evidence in this case.
- You can't go in there.

521
00:36:46,010 --> 00:36:47,010
Sir.

522
00:36:54,050 --> 00:36:55,696
Should we force our way in?

523
00:36:55,720 --> 00:36:58,520
You know this is
obstructing justice, right?

524
00:37:21,110 --> 00:37:23,050
Let's move!

525
00:37:35,630 --> 00:37:37,530
(Police)

526
00:37:39,830 --> 00:37:41,710
Mujin Police Public
Services desk. How can I...

527
00:37:43,630 --> 00:37:44,607
What brings you here?

528
00:37:44,631 --> 00:37:46,670
I came to talk about the
Joint Investigation HQ,

529
00:37:47,240 --> 00:37:48,340
but what's all this?

530
00:37:48,640 --> 00:37:52,140
It's nothing. I was put on standby,
so they just have me here for now.

531
00:37:52,210 --> 00:37:54,516
- Once the internal audit is over...
- Right.

532
00:37:54,540 --> 00:37:56,926
An internal audit? They
pulled you off the case,

533
00:37:56,950 --> 00:37:58,410
and stuck you here as retaliation.

534
00:37:58,810 --> 00:38:01,050
Calm down. Getting
worked up is bad for you.

535
00:38:01,120 --> 00:38:02,690
Let's go. We can talk outside.

536
00:38:09,060 --> 00:38:10,300
What do you think you're doing?

537
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:16,900
Sit down. I had some porridge
made for you to soothe your stomach.

538
00:38:16,970 --> 00:38:18,050
The Joint Investigation HQ.

539
00:38:18,700 --> 00:38:19,970
I know you're behind this, Mom.

540
00:38:23,240 --> 00:38:24,480
You should have seen it coming.

541
00:38:24,940 --> 00:38:28,080
You were just circling the
case without any hard evidence.

542
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:31,750
Didn't it occur to you that
the tables could be turned?

543
00:38:32,110 --> 00:38:35,950
Who would've thought my own mother
would be pushing me to the edge?

544
00:38:37,090 --> 00:38:40,820
We've never been on the
same side, but this is different.

545
00:38:41,020 --> 00:38:42,830
Mom, you targeted me.

546
00:38:43,890 --> 00:38:45,760
Why would you go this far?

547
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:50,700
I just did what I've always done.

548
00:38:51,530 --> 00:38:53,240
What I know how to do.

549
00:38:53,370 --> 00:38:56,240
For Haeil? For your clients?

550
00:38:58,110 --> 00:38:59,110
That's right.

551
00:39:01,880 --> 00:39:04,210
Then I guess I'll just do
what I've always done.

552
00:39:06,020 --> 00:39:07,180
What I have to do.

553
00:39:13,590 --> 00:39:16,360
Thank you for proving
that I was right, Mom.

554
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:19,310
Haeil must be eradicated from this country.

555
00:39:23,230 --> 00:39:24,600
Be careful of Baek Tae Joo.

556
00:39:25,200 --> 00:39:27,370
He has us both you and me

557
00:39:28,100 --> 00:39:30,170
in the palm of his hand.

558
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:34,340
What is that supposed to mean?

559
00:39:34,510 --> 00:39:37,780
I just hope that I'm wrong about this.

560
00:39:40,550 --> 00:39:41,790
Make sure you eat the porridge.

561
00:39:56,230 --> 00:39:58,730
(Boarding House)

562
00:40:09,350 --> 00:40:12,280
(Please keep quiet indoors.)

563
00:41:43,270 --> 00:41:46,280
It's safe here. Don't
worry, and come on in.

564
00:41:57,920 --> 00:42:00,790
Remember what I told you on the way here.

565
00:42:01,190 --> 00:42:04,090
Everyone, keep outside
contact to a minimum.

566
00:42:04,360 --> 00:42:07,060
And don't tell anyone you're here.

567
00:42:07,860 --> 00:42:09,470
Park Je Yeol is on the run,

568
00:42:09,730 --> 00:42:12,600
and we don't know what
those users will try to pull.

569
00:42:12,770 --> 00:42:14,400
- Okay.
- Right.

570
00:42:15,240 --> 00:42:17,140
I'll show you to your rooms. Follow me.

571
00:42:53,210 --> 00:42:54,210
Darn.

572
00:43:09,490 --> 00:43:12,490
There are two ways we can do this.

573
00:43:13,530 --> 00:43:14,560
First,

574
00:43:15,060 --> 00:43:17,600
we silence you for good.

575
00:43:20,140 --> 00:43:23,510
Second, we give you one last chance

576
00:43:23,570 --> 00:43:25,240
to make up for all this.

577
00:43:27,210 --> 00:43:29,350
Which one would you prefer we choose?

578
00:43:30,650 --> 00:43:32,410
What are you trying to say?

579
00:43:33,920 --> 00:43:36,590
That I should take the fall for all of you,

580
00:43:37,250 --> 00:43:38,690
and go down alone?

581
00:43:39,320 --> 00:43:42,220
Either way, I'm the only one
who gets screwed in the end.

582
00:43:44,160 --> 00:43:45,860
The deal doesn't add up.

583
00:43:46,660 --> 00:43:48,900
We'll make sure you
won't be in prison for long.

584
00:43:51,070 --> 00:43:52,100
How long?

585
00:43:55,340 --> 00:43:58,740
Once this storm blows
over, you'll be a free man.

586
00:44:00,110 --> 00:44:02,510
And we'll provide a hefty
sum for your troubles.

587
00:44:19,360 --> 00:44:21,236
I'll be at Seoul Central
District Prosecutors' Office

588
00:44:21,260 --> 00:44:22,400
by 2pm.

589
00:44:25,830 --> 00:44:29,870
We're live. Prosecutor Park Je
Yeol, a key Connect In case operator,

590
00:44:29,940 --> 00:44:32,740
has announced that he will
voluntarily surrender himself

591
00:44:32,810 --> 00:44:33,940
to the prosecution.

592
00:44:34,380 --> 00:44:36,356
Could you please comment
on the current situation?

593
00:44:36,380 --> 00:44:37,880
Prosecutor, could we get a statement?

594
00:44:38,580 --> 00:44:40,780
(Prosecutors' Office)

595
00:44:44,450 --> 00:44:45,450
First of all,

596
00:44:46,020 --> 00:44:48,360
I sincerely apologise to the public,

597
00:44:49,090 --> 00:44:50,430
for causing so much concern.

598
00:44:52,630 --> 00:44:53,830
As for the Connect In app,

599
00:44:54,800 --> 00:44:57,270
I was the one who operated it.

600
00:44:58,600 --> 00:45:00,080
Are you admitting to all the charges?

601
00:45:00,240 --> 00:45:02,970
Is the VIP list claimed by LnJ authentic?

602
00:45:03,770 --> 00:45:06,010
I abused my position as a prosecutor

603
00:45:06,880 --> 00:45:10,110
to make a mockery of the
law and to profit improperly.

604
00:45:11,580 --> 00:45:15,420
To the victims irreparably
harmed in the process,

605
00:45:15,620 --> 00:45:17,350
I have committed a grave sin.

606
00:45:18,490 --> 00:45:21,260
However, the list that LnJ released,

607
00:45:21,660 --> 00:45:24,090
the so-called "VIP list,"

608
00:45:24,830 --> 00:45:26,300
is completely false...

609
00:45:27,830 --> 00:45:28,960
What's going on?

610
00:45:29,360 --> 00:45:31,070
- What is this?
- What?

611
00:45:31,770 --> 00:45:33,340
- What is this?
- What?

612
00:45:33,570 --> 00:45:34,716
- What are they doing?
- That's disgusting.

613
00:45:34,740 --> 00:45:35,740
Are they kissing?

614
00:45:36,370 --> 00:45:37,910
- What is that?
- What's happening?

615
00:45:38,240 --> 00:45:40,480
These videos are being
posted on social media right now.

616
00:45:40,840 --> 00:45:42,010
Care to explain?

617
00:45:43,680 --> 00:45:44,680
(Today's bombshell)

618
00:45:44,780 --> 00:45:46,780
Please help me.

619
00:45:47,220 --> 00:45:49,850
I was brought here against my will.

620
00:45:50,620 --> 00:45:52,690
- Please.
- Darn it.

621
00:45:54,190 --> 00:45:56,466
- Give us a statement!
- Prosecutor, are you running away?

622
00:45:56,490 --> 00:45:58,560
- Prosecutor, a statement!
- Sir!

623
00:45:58,630 --> 00:46:01,030
- Prosecutor, wait!
- Please explain!

624
00:46:01,100 --> 00:46:02,800
- Prosecutor!
- Where are you going?

625
00:46:02,870 --> 00:46:04,500
- Was it all a lie?
- Is it true?

626
00:46:04,570 --> 00:46:06,340
- Prosecutor!
- What's going on?

627
00:46:06,600 --> 00:46:08,246
You said you'd turn yourself
in. Why are you running away?

628
00:46:08,270 --> 00:46:09,470
Are you running away?

629
00:46:10,870 --> 00:46:12,040
Are you running away?

630
00:46:12,410 --> 00:46:13,410
Prosecutor!

631
00:46:16,880 --> 00:46:17,880
This is insane.

632
00:46:21,750 --> 00:46:22,780
What is this?

633
00:46:23,320 --> 00:46:24,320
Hey.

634
00:46:25,350 --> 00:46:26,720
Put more emotion into your voice.

635
00:46:27,560 --> 00:46:29,400
I told you, sound more
desperate when you sob.

636
00:46:30,390 --> 00:46:31,890
That's more my taste.

637
00:46:32,390 --> 00:46:34,860
Ye Ji, did you see the videos they posted?

638
00:46:35,430 --> 00:46:37,200
You can see all the victims' faces.

639
00:46:37,570 --> 00:46:38,976
- Report it and take it down...
- Everyone, come on out.

640
00:46:39,000 --> 00:46:40,676
- As fast as you can.
- Turn off your phones,

641
00:46:40,700 --> 00:46:41,970
and stay off the internet.

642
00:46:46,780 --> 00:46:47,780
Attorney Yoon.

643
00:46:57,850 --> 00:47:01,160
(Connect In Evidence Video four)

644
00:47:02,890 --> 00:47:05,090
You think that's all I have on you?

645
00:47:05,560 --> 00:47:07,240
You're the one who escalated this, not me.

646
00:47:07,900 --> 00:47:08,960
That little jerk.

647
00:47:10,230 --> 00:47:11,870
(Park Je Yeol, Mujin District Prosecutor)

648
00:47:13,000 --> 00:47:14,640
(Park Je Yeol, Mujin District Prosecutor)

649
00:47:16,570 --> 00:47:19,446
- You dare screw me over like this?
- It wasn't me.

650
00:47:19,470 --> 00:47:20,910
I also have no idea.

651
00:47:21,480 --> 00:47:23,310
I have no idea how any of this happened.

652
00:47:23,650 --> 00:47:26,010
All these videos were shot on our phones.

653
00:47:26,950 --> 00:47:29,350
If you didn't tamper with
our phones then who did?

654
00:47:29,750 --> 00:47:32,650
Who else could've secretly
filmed and leaked this trash?

655
00:47:33,020 --> 00:47:34,120
I'll find out who did it.

656
00:47:34,790 --> 00:47:37,930
I'll quickly find out who did this and why...

657
00:47:37,990 --> 00:47:38,990
Shut it.

658
00:47:39,560 --> 00:47:41,760
I'm about to teach you what
a fate worse than death

659
00:47:43,170 --> 00:47:44,230
really is.

660
00:48:36,450 --> 00:48:37,920
I just don't understand.

661
00:48:38,450 --> 00:48:39,450
This makes no sense.

662
00:48:40,190 --> 00:48:42,160
If Park Je Yeol didn't post it, who did?

663
00:48:42,660 --> 00:48:45,930
Think about it. Why would
he suddenly surrender?

664
00:48:46,660 --> 00:48:49,180
He must've gotten his story
straight with the other assailants.

665
00:48:51,330 --> 00:48:54,370
But did you see it? How he
panicked when he saw the video?

666
00:48:55,440 --> 00:48:57,540
You think that cunning
jerk would just throw away

667
00:48:57,770 --> 00:48:59,680
his only lifeline like that?

668
00:49:13,460 --> 00:49:14,460
Attorney...

669
00:49:15,260 --> 00:49:16,260
We

670
00:49:17,160 --> 00:49:18,690
Can't do this anymore.

671
00:49:20,960 --> 00:49:23,270
- Su Eun.
- Our voices,

672
00:49:23,630 --> 00:49:25,370
the brief glimpses of our faces...

673
00:49:25,670 --> 00:49:27,600
People are already going crazy online

674
00:49:28,340 --> 00:49:30,440
trying to identify us.

675
00:49:31,310 --> 00:49:34,016
We'll do whatever we can
to stop secondary harm.

676
00:49:34,040 --> 00:49:35,080
All we wanted

677
00:49:36,010 --> 00:49:38,780
was to go back to our normal lives.

678
00:49:39,980 --> 00:49:44,420
We believed punishing those
men was the only way we could.

679
00:49:45,990 --> 00:49:48,490
But now, it feels like
it was all for nothing.

680
00:49:52,190 --> 00:49:54,530
Just releasing that one audio file

681
00:49:55,030 --> 00:49:56,800
took us two sleepless nights.

682
00:49:58,100 --> 00:49:59,130
But

683
00:50:00,070 --> 00:50:02,800
the whole world has seen it, Attorney.

684
00:50:03,470 --> 00:50:05,270
What they did to us.

685
00:50:11,610 --> 00:50:12,610
All right.

686
00:50:13,920 --> 00:50:15,120
I'll give you all a ride.

687
00:50:15,950 --> 00:50:19,290
But you have to pick up
when I call, at least once a day.

688
00:50:19,550 --> 00:50:21,230
If you don't, I'm coming to hunt you down.

689
00:50:23,390 --> 00:50:26,700
And don't forget. You're
always welcome here.

690
00:50:30,370 --> 00:50:32,770
I'll start the car. Grab your
things and come on out.

691
00:50:43,750 --> 00:50:44,910
Where's that wench?

692
00:50:46,920 --> 00:50:49,790
That wench. Where is that crazy wench?

693
00:50:53,820 --> 00:50:54,820
What's going on?

694
00:50:57,260 --> 00:50:59,800
- What are you talking about?
- Han Min Seo, that wench.

695
00:51:00,400 --> 00:51:01,930
You're hiding her, aren't you?

696
00:51:02,630 --> 00:51:04,330
She told me everything herself.

697
00:51:10,370 --> 00:51:12,210
Recognise me?

698
00:51:12,770 --> 00:51:15,740
Those brass knuckles.
You're going to regret all of this.

699
00:51:16,280 --> 00:51:18,850
You're going to regret
everything you've ever done.

700
00:51:19,050 --> 00:51:20,220
Even the day you were born.

701
00:51:21,250 --> 00:51:22,420
Even the day you were born.

702
00:51:24,420 --> 00:51:25,420
You...

703
00:51:27,260 --> 00:51:29,620
Those videos? I'm the one who posted them.

704
00:51:30,960 --> 00:51:32,360
I bet you're wondering how.

705
00:51:32,990 --> 00:51:34,100
Where are you right now?

706
00:51:34,530 --> 00:51:36,130
If you want to know, come and find me.

707
00:51:37,100 --> 00:51:38,200
I'll send you my location.

708
00:51:42,100 --> 00:51:43,270
What do you mean?

709
00:51:45,770 --> 00:51:49,510
Han Min Seo was the one
who posted the videos? Not you?

710
00:51:49,950 --> 00:51:51,630
I didn't even know the darn thing existed.

711
00:51:52,150 --> 00:51:53,650
So, where is that wench?

712
00:51:54,180 --> 00:51:55,420
Where is she?

713
00:51:57,220 --> 00:51:59,520
Oh, right.

714
00:52:00,090 --> 00:52:02,090
You're all here together.

715
00:52:02,890 --> 00:52:05,630
Perfect. Now I can
take you all out at once.

716
00:52:08,360 --> 00:52:10,170
Is he here for us?

717
00:52:10,230 --> 00:52:12,570
Call the police, now. I'll get them inside.

718
00:52:16,370 --> 00:52:17,770
You put her up to this, didn't you?

719
00:52:18,140 --> 00:52:20,940
Trying to get revenge on me? Is that it?

720
00:52:22,640 --> 00:52:24,550
You put her up to it, right?

721
00:52:26,880 --> 00:52:30,020
I knew something was off. That's it.

722
00:52:30,450 --> 00:52:31,850
It was a trap.

723
00:52:32,190 --> 00:52:34,420
This was all a setup
from the start, wasn't it?

724
00:52:35,020 --> 00:52:36,020
Right?

725
00:52:43,500 --> 00:52:46,740
This piece of trash still doesn't get it.

726
00:52:46,900 --> 00:52:49,870
Yes. You were there too, right?

727
00:52:58,280 --> 00:52:59,950
You ruined everything.

728
00:53:00,750 --> 00:53:01,750
You hear me?

729
00:53:03,220 --> 00:53:06,860
You wenches ruined everything! You hear me?

730
00:53:09,590 --> 00:53:10,590
I'll end this.

731
00:55:01,470 --> 00:55:05,110
Someone's been hurt.

732
00:55:17,620 --> 00:55:18,620
(Attorney Yoon Ra Young)

733
00:55:18,690 --> 00:55:19,990
(Thank you...)

734
00:55:24,060 --> 00:55:25,360
Thank you, Mom,

735
00:55:26,090 --> 00:55:27,330
for killing Dad.

736
00:55:54,290 --> 00:55:58,290
The safest way to dispose of a
bomb that's served its purpose

737
00:56:07,040 --> 00:56:09,100
is to just go ahead and pull the pin.

738
00:56:18,280 --> 00:56:19,850
(CEO Baek Tae Joo)

739
00:56:19,910 --> 00:56:21,220
(The Prime)

740
00:56:27,760 --> 00:56:29,260
It's infested.

741
00:56:29,690 --> 00:56:32,430
If I leave it, it will
contaminate the whole thing.

742
00:56:33,360 --> 00:56:34,730
So, you use pesticides?

743
00:56:35,600 --> 00:56:38,430
Rather than that, I lure
them with the trap pests like.

744
00:56:40,270 --> 00:56:41,340
The pests

745
00:56:41,740 --> 00:56:43,910
take the bait without
ever knowing it's a trap.

746
00:57:08,560 --> 00:57:12,530
(Honour)

747
00:58:04,150 --> 00:58:05,390
I won't say rest in peace.

748
00:58:05,790 --> 00:58:08,820
- You're in the fiery pit anyway.
- Find Han Min Seo.

749
00:58:09,090 --> 00:58:11,960
She's the one who lured
Park Je Yeol to the villa too.

750
00:58:12,390 --> 00:58:13,390
I'm sorry.

751
00:58:14,260 --> 00:58:15,930
This has gone on long enough.

752
00:58:16,500 --> 00:58:18,070
Stop Ra Young from being released.

753
00:58:18,270 --> 00:58:20,770
We can't prove self-defence
without eyewitness testimony.

754
00:58:21,140 --> 00:58:25,070
You just ruined my whole life, Mom!

755
00:58:25,970 --> 00:58:27,410
I have to get out of here.

756
00:58:28,040 --> 00:58:30,350
There's someone behind Min Seo.
